SAME GRACE   Matthew 20:1-16


The parable of the workers in the vineyard demonstrating that those who are first will be last and those who are last will be first in the Kingdom of Heaven, can be used to demonstrate grace. We all get the same grace, the death of JESUS to pay a for our sins. The same grace for the rich and poor, wicked and ‘good’, evil and ‘nice’, the social stalwarts and the outcast. JESUS can’t love us anymore or any less than He does right now. The one who was a Christian from childhood and the sinner who converts with their last breath – same grace.
